.sp 3mm
Coverage is conditional upon no more than ten people travelling together.
.sp 3mm
The insurance only covers expenses that apply to the cardholder and
his/her spouse or partner and children, see Article 1.0. This means
that if several people are travelling or living together, the expenses
for transport, accommodation etc. will be divided proportionally.
.sp 3mm
A travelling companion is defined as: A person who booked travel
together with the insured with the intention of completing the
journey in the company of same. If the names of the insured and
his/her companion do not appear on the same travel documents or
similar, Privatsikring will determine whether the other person
can be considered a travelling companion on the basis of the
information presented.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.* ---------------------
