18.4 Reporting claims
:SKRSLUT.
.br
In the event of a claim, the following documentation is to be submitted to
Privatsikring:
.of 5mm
*¤The demands from the travel organiser - documented in writing - together
with the terms and conditions for purchasing the travel.
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤Documentation for expenses paid for transport, rental of holiday
accommodation, planned activities etc. as well as documentation stating
that these expenses cannot be refunded.
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤Unused plane tickets, coach tickets and the like.
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤Doctor's note and copy of the patient journal that describes in
detail the treatment procedure and, if appropriate, death
certificate, only in the event of acute illness, injury or death.
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤Copy of police report only in the event of burglary, fire or fraudulent
actions
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤if the travel organiser was not informed of the cancellation immediately
after the occurrence of an event covered by the insurance
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤if the reason for cancellation existed when the travel was ordered or on
payment of the deposit
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤if the illness/injury or other reason for cancellation already existed
when the travel/deposit was paid
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤lost holiday purpose. This is taken to mean that the insured is affected
by a sudden illness or injury that prevents him/her from completing the
main activity planned for the holiday. For example, this may take the form
of an inner ear infection prior to a diving holiday, or a broken finger
prior to a golfing holiday.
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤expenses that are reimbursed by the travel organiser
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤expenses for a doctor's note and/or other documentation
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤expenses that the insured has paid for persons who are not covered by
the insurance. This also applies even if the insured has paid their
share of the travel.
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤childbirth or consequences of pregnancy within one month of the forecast
date of birth
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤pregnancy issues in general
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤if the insured has declined medical treatment of an illness/injury, or
if medical treatment has been discontinued
